この表は，建築基準法に基づき建築主から知事に届出のあった建築工事届により，着工住宅を工事別に分類したもので，「新設」とは建築物の新築，増築又は改築によって住宅の戸が新たに造られる工事をいい，「その他」とは住宅が増築又は改築されるときで，住宅戸数が新たに増加しない工事をいう。

This table refers to the number of dwelling constructions started after submission of construction notification to the Governor by the builders as prescribed in the Building Standards Act， which have been classified by type of construction.   "Newly constructed" refers to the building of a new dwelling unit through new construction， extension， or reconstruction， and  "Others" refers to extension or reconstruction that does not result in an increase of dwelling units.
